11
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,940
[Episode 27]

12
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:33,240
[Jiang Si, the daughter
of the Count of Dongping]

13
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,750
Why did Imperial Concubine Xian

14
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,720
invite a lady

15
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,030
like Jiang Si?

16
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,960
It wasn't you?

17
00:01:43,030 --> 00:01:44,470
Why would I do that?

18
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,880
Background and personality
are far more important

19
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,600
than having good looks.

20
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:53,240
Imperial Concubine Xian is going

21
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,960
to match Prince Yan

22
00:01:55,390 --> 00:01:56,600
with a lowborn consort.

23
00:01:58,080 --> 00:02:00,310
But, she shouldn't pick
the woman whose engagement

24
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:01,080
was annulled

25
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:02,270
by the Duke's family.

26
00:02:02,870 --> 00:02:05,390
I heard Imperial Concubine Xian
was cruel to Prince Yan,

27
00:02:05,990 --> 00:02:07,640
showing him no motherly love whatsoever.

28
00:02:08,389 --> 00:02:10,389
I finally witnessed it for myself.

29
00:02:18,670 --> 00:02:21,990
Does Princess Consort Zhuang
want a peerless beauty

30
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:24,079
as Prince Shu's concubine?

31
00:02:25,390 --> 00:02:26,360
However,

32
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:29,829
there is a proper procedure for that.

33
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,640
It's not right to pick one

34
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,320
while selecting a principal consort.

35
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,520
During the Floral Banquet,

36
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,150
I gave the peonies

37
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,920
to six women.

38
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,550
But deep down, I only wanted

39
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,670
Qingrong to have it.

40
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:54,640
You and the late Empress

41
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:56,870
were a match made in heaven.

42
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,200
Everyone envied you.

43
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,710
In a blink of an eye,

44
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:04,640
it's been years since she passed.

45
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:06,430
Your Majesty,

46
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,920
Yang Nianzhi
of the Directorate of Astronomy is here.

47
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,040
Send him in.

48
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,430
Your Majesty.

49
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:16,240
Your Highness.

50
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:17,990
Before the princes' wedding,

51
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:19,200
we routinely

52
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:21,920
calculated the feasibility
of the marriage.

53
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,480
These are the results

54
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,040
for Prince Shu and Prince Yan.

55
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,390
Please have a look.

56
00:03:28,550 --> 00:03:30,640
Prince Yan's fate carries ill fortune.

57
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,710
His life is one of adversity.

58
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,150
He must never marry

59
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,520
[Yang Nianzhi, Directorate of Astronomy]
a woman with a life of desolation.

60
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,670
The union of the two

61
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:40,200
brings harm to the nation
and the families.

62
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,480
It could be a great calamity.

63
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,710
Prince Yan saved my life

64
00:03:45,110 --> 00:03:46,360
in the nick of time.

65
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,590
Do you still declare him

66
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,829
a prince of ill fate?

67
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:50,270
But...

68
00:03:50,270 --> 00:03:51,150
Supervisor Yang.

69
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:52,829
He is a prince.

70
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,200
Does the Directorate of Astronomy
have jurisdiction over

71
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:56,640
his birth

72
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,320
and his marriage?

73
00:03:59,990 --> 00:04:01,640
My brother has promised Prince Yan

74
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,760
he could pick the woman he likes.

75
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:05,760
So, spare us

76
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:06,990
your baseless claims.

77
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:07,920
Your Majesty,

78
00:04:08,270 --> 00:04:10,030
we're responsible
for aligning palace affairs

79
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,680
with Heaven's will.

80
00:04:12,230 --> 00:04:13,590
Controlling the prince is not our goal.

81
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,200
You!

82
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:16,680
The result is the work
of countless calculations.

83
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,560
We can prove our claims.

84
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,910
Hence, it's not baseless.

85
00:04:24,150 --> 00:04:24,710
Enough.

86
00:04:25,230 --> 00:04:27,390
He carried out his duty.

87
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,150
Rest assured.

88
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:33,880
Only noble ladies were invited

89
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,909
to the Floral Banquet.

90
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:38,390
How could any of them
carry desolation in their fate?

91
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:39,640
Never mind.

92
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,350
Supervisor Yang.

93
00:04:42,030 --> 00:04:42,680
Yes.

94
00:04:42,909 --> 00:04:44,150
When the banquet is over,

95
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,710
check the background

96
00:04:46,150 --> 00:04:48,000
of every lady
who receives the gift flower.

97
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,200
Your Majesty's decision is most wise.

98
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,909
I take my leave now.

