00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:38,600
Miss Jiang is a fine candidate.

577
00:27:39,230 --> 00:27:39,990
Your Majesty!

578
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:42,200
I had it examined.

579
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:45,310
The name Miss Jiang hid in the flowers

580
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:47,160
was "Yu Jin."

581
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:50,200
It's clear they feel connected.

582
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:52,750
Why not give them your blessing?

583
00:27:53,230 --> 00:27:54,750
Perhaps you're unaware.

584
00:27:55,160 --> 00:27:55,840
Miss Jiang

585
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,510
once annulled an engagement
with the son

586
00:27:57,550 --> 00:27:58,230
of the Duke of Anguo.

587
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:00,270
Is that so?

588
00:28:00,270 --> 00:28:01,990
That is not a serious matter.

589
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,710
In the past, an empress

590
00:28:04,030 --> 00:28:05,510
was even married

591
00:28:05,990 --> 00:28:06,990
and had two kids

592
00:28:06,990 --> 00:28:08,440
with her former husband.

593
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,550
In the end,

594
00:28:10,790 --> 00:28:13,510
she and the emperor
brought prosperity to the realm.

595
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,550
And she was lauded for her deeds.

596
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,360
That is not the same.

597
00:28:17,510 --> 00:28:18,070
Dear,

598
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:20,270
it's Jin's consort,

599
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:22,270
not the Crown Prince's.

600
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,230
As long as he is happy,

601
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:25,510
that's enough.

602
00:28:26,230 --> 00:28:27,360
Look at the bright side.

603
00:28:29,070 --> 00:28:30,510
Isn't it fun to have

604
00:28:30,510 --> 00:28:32,270
a daughter-in-law
who knows magic tricks

605
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,790
to cheer you up?

606
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,920
I am mad

607
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:38,680
because he should've told me

608
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:40,470
before making these decisions.

609
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:42,470
He disregarded all of that.

610
00:28:42,990 --> 00:28:43,600
Does he even

611
00:28:43,710 --> 00:28:45,120
have any respect for his mother?

612
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:47,310
I have an idea.

613
00:28:48,310 --> 00:28:50,920
I'll see what's Jin's take
on the matter.

614
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:59,400
Father. Mother.

615
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:00,640
Jin.

616
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,920
You said Miss Jiang was to your liking.

617
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:05,360
Do you intend to marry her?

618
00:29:05,750 --> 00:29:06,550
Father,

619
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:07,840
you read my thoughts.

620
00:29:08,070 --> 00:29:09,510
But she annulled an engagement.

621
00:29:10,600 --> 00:29:12,200
You don't mind it now.

622
00:29:12,470 --> 00:29:13,270
But what if

623
00:29:13,470 --> 00:29:14,470
you regret it?

624
00:29:14,600 --> 00:29:15,640
Will you blame me

625
00:29:15,750 --> 00:29:17,160
for not upholding my promise?

626
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:18,600
Convince me

627
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:20,750
as to why her past doesn't bother you.

628
00:29:21,750 --> 00:29:23,790
A gem overlooked by the blind

629
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:25,990
can still be cherished by the one

630
00:29:25,990 --> 00:29:27,120
who knows its worth.

631
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,470
Very well.

632
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:32,680
I'll grant you the wish.

633
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:34,640
You may make Miss Jiang
your principal consort.

634
00:29:35,470 --> 00:29:36,440
Many thanks, Father.

635
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:39,790
Many thanks to you too, Mother.

636
00:29:41,120 --> 00:29:42,990
This decision is your responsibility.

637
00:29:43,270 --> 00:29:44,840
Whatever the future holds for you,

638
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:46,880
you must endure it.

639
00:29:55,070 --> 00:29:55,960
Don't worry.

640
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:57,880
I will be happy.

641
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:58,960
Go now.

642
00:29:59,470 --> 00:30:00,750
I'll take my leave now.

643
00:30:07,310 --> 00:30:08,710
See how thrilled he is?

644
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:11,550
This boy is just too straightforward.

645
00:30:12,470 --> 00:30:13,840
He can't contain his emotions.

646
00:30:13,990 --> 00:30:14,710
I am concerned

647
00:30:14,710 --> 00:30:16,070
about his best interests.

648
00:30:17,840 --> 00:30:19,470
And that made me the villain?

649
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:21,440
You're overthinking.

650
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:24,400
I'll leave Jin's wedding

651
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:26,750
in your capable hands.

652
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:29,400
He will understand your effort

653
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:30,550
sooner or later.

654
00:30:30,990 --> 00:30:31,440
But I...

655
00:30:36,550 --> 00:30:37,400
You may stay.

656
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:49,640
That silly brat.

657
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,200
He is too blunt.

658
00:30:51,550 --> 00:30:53,470
Even if he adores her,

659
00:30:54,030 --> 00:30:55,550
he could express
his affection more subtly.

660
00:30:56,030 --> 00:30:57,750
Prince Yan has a pure heart.

661
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:01,120
He is a young man
with confidence and enthusiasm.

662
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:04,510
It's hard not to express
his true feelings.

663
00:31:07,750 --> 00:31:08,470
Very well.

664
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:11,070
All six flowers for one girl.

665
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,750
He did the exact same thing

666
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,230
I was too afraid to even try.

667
00:31:19,010 --> 00:31:20,980
[Count of Dongping's Mansion]

668
00:31:20,990 --> 00:31:21,840
Si.

669
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:24,160
You received six flowers

670
00:31:24,470 --> 00:31:25,990
at the Floral Banquet last night?

671
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,710
You've made our family proud.

672
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:33,750
So, who were they from?

673
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:36,880
Prince Yan.

674
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:37,640
Anyone else?

675
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:41,200
Nothing more.

676
00:31:41,790 --> 00:31:42,960
They were all from Prince Yan.

677
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:51,160
This bodes trouble.

678
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,880
How so, Grandmother?

679
00:31:53,990 --> 00:31:56,160
"The nail that sticks out
gets hammered."

680
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,960
Don't you understand that?

681
00:31:58,230 --> 00:31:59,680
You outshone the others.

682
00:31:59,840 --> 00:32:01,070
That will garner jealousy.

683
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,680
Even our family

684
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,790
will be at the center of criticism.

685
00:32:04,990 --> 00:32:05,550
Mother!

686
00:32:06,990 --> 00:32:07,470
Mother!

687
00:32:07,710 --> 00:32:08,600
What is it?

688
00:32:09,990 --> 00:32:10,440
Mother.

689
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:14,750
Rumors are spreading.

690
00:32:15,750 --> 00:32:17,230
They're targeting Miss Si.

691
00:32:17,510 --> 00:32:18,550
She's being called
a bringer of ill fortune.

692
00:32:18,990 --> 00:32:20,310
They say regardless of any favor shown,

693
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:23,400
the royal family
will never acknowledge her.

694
00:32:23,710 --> 00:32:25,440
They say we're naive

695
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:27,270
to think our girls

696
00:32:27,470 --> 00:32:28,440
can rise to prominence and become great.

697
00:32:31,470 --> 00:32:32,680
Si, did you hear that?

698
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:33,360
Do you know

699
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:35,310
how people see you?

700
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:38,510
You are too young and naive.

701
00:32:39,550 --> 00:32:41,270
You should've been more reserved.

702
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:42,990
Yield when necessary.

703
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,510
Don't you know that?

704
00:32:44,710 --> 00:32:45,990
If no one is embarrassed,

705
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:48,160
then everyone can be on good terms
with each other.

706
00:32:50,230 --> 00:32:51,270
Indeed.

707
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,470
I will obey you

708
00:32:52,840 --> 00:32:54,120
if it's anything else,

709
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,840
but when it comes to my marriage,

710
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,440
I won't hold back.

711
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:00,790
Think it through.

712
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,230
If he marries you,

713
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:03,470
all is well.

714
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:04,600
But what if he doesn't?

715
00:33:04,750 --> 00:33:05,920
You will bring

716
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:07,990
tremendous shame to this family!

717
00:33:10,470 --> 00:33:11,120
Enough.

718
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:13,710
For the time being,

719
00:33:14,070 --> 00:33:15,470
stay in

720
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:16,120
your room,

721
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,070
reflect on this

722
00:33:17,310 --> 00:33:18,880
and tone down your temper.

723
00:33:19,990 --> 00:33:21,120
I don't want people to think

724
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:22,550
that we are overstepping

725
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:23,750
boundaries.

726
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:27,710
Yes.

727
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,070
I'll take my leave.

728
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:34,790
Mother, calm down.

729
00:33:35,230 --> 00:33:35,880
Take it easy.

730
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:37,270
I've been thinking.

731
00:33:37,790 --> 00:33:40,120
If he marries the prince,

732
00:33:40,470 --> 00:33:41,510
I should be happy.

733
00:33:41,550 --> 00:33:43,680
I want the girls
to marry great husbands.

734
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:44,550
But...

735
00:33:45,710 --> 00:33:47,920
Noble families
could be riddled with perils.

736
00:33:47,990 --> 00:33:49,750
Mother, you are right.

737
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:52,030
Who knew

738
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:54,840
Commandant Yu was actually Prince Yan?

739
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:55,790
Ever since

740
00:33:55,840 --> 00:33:57,400
she got close to Prince Yan,

741
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:59,600
she's been acting recklessly.

742
00:34:01,840 --> 00:34:02,800
Mother, calm down.

743
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:11,110
I told you.

744
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:12,670
She shouldn't marry the prince.

745
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,840
You are endangering her!

746
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:16,510
Mingyue fell in love
with the Seventh Prince.

747
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:18,070
There is nothing I can do.

748
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:19,469
Very well.

749
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,469
The Seventh Prince gave all six flowers

750
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:22,719
to Jiang Si alone.

751
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:24,070
Mingyue saw it for herself.

752
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:24,989
She should give up.

753
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,760
The flowers meant nothing.

754
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,320
I put meticulous effort

755
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,320
into the Floral Banquet.

756
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:33,630
Yet, Jiang Si was unappreciative.

757
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:35,469
What a shame.

758
00:34:36,190 --> 00:34:37,840
I almost got her punished.

759
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:42,630
As expected from Su Ke's daughter.

760
00:34:43,550 --> 00:34:44,510
Just like her mother,

761
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,920
Jiang Si is trouble.

762
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:50,960
What?

763
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:53,760
Wasn't it enough

764
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,550
that you took Su Ke from me?

765
00:34:55,989 --> 00:34:57,400
And now you want Mingyue

766
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:59,240
to steal the love of her daughter?

767
00:34:59,510 --> 00:35:01,150
Is Mingyue your daughter,

768
00:35:01,630 --> 00:35:03,720
or is it

769
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:04,360
that cursed Jiang Si?

770
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,590
Cut the nonsense!

771
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,590
Feeling guilty?

772
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,190
Did I touch a nerve?

773
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:13,990
No wonder there are rumors

774
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:16,510
that Su Ke and you have been so intimate

775
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:18,110
that she lost her purity long ago.

776
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:21,720
Perhaps the rumors are true.

777
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:23,320
Rong Yang.

778
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:26,920
That was out of line.

779
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:30,760
There was nothing between Su Ke and I.

780
00:35:31,470 --> 00:35:33,280
She's been dead for years.

781
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:34,590
Must you tarnish her reputation?

782
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,400
How vile are you?

783
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:37,630
Silence!

784
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,030
You dare yell at me

785
00:35:39,030 --> 00:35:40,030
over a dead woman?

786
00:35:55,510 --> 00:35:56,030
Pretty.

787
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,070
So pretty.

788
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,800
This flower looks like you.

789
00:36:03,070 --> 00:36:03,550
It's Her Highness.

790
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:11,990
- I'm sorry.
- Please forgive me, Your Highness.

791
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,030
Raise your head.

792
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,920
- Please have mercy!
- Please forgive me!

793
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:34,190
Please!

794
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:36,960
Bring me the torch!

795
00:37:07,550 --> 00:37:08,190
Mother.

796
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,760
Mingyue.

797
00:37:16,990 --> 00:37:19,110
When a man doesn't love you,

798
00:37:20,030 --> 00:37:21,840
all of his finest qualities

799
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:24,400
are meaningless to you.

800
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:26,280
But I've seen

801
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:27,440
his finest qualities.

802
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:31,590
If I can't have him,

803
00:37:32,470 --> 00:37:36,110
then I shall never have peace.

804
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:37,880
There are things

805
00:37:39,030 --> 00:37:40,320
you can't have

806
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:42,630
if you seize it by force.

807
00:37:43,720 --> 00:37:44,510
But Mother,

808
00:37:46,070 --> 00:37:47,360
if I could do it again,

809
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:49,720
I would

810
00:37:49,720 --> 00:37:50,880
make the same choice.

811
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,550
How can I swallow it

812
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:54,150
without first fighting for it?

813
00:37:58,190 --> 00:38:00,190
Mother, please have faith in me.

814
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:03,150
I can change it.

815
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:08,670
You couldn't get what you yearned for.

816
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,150
Perhaps I could.

817
00:38:18,410 --> 00:38:22,510
[Chengtian Hall]

818
00:38:38,990 --> 00:38:40,110
Your Highness.

819
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:42,590
I must

820
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:45,320
thank you for saving me, General Cui.

821
00:38:45,550 --> 00:38:46,920
It was my duty.

822
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:56,880
Greetings, Your Majesty.

823
00:38:57,590 --> 00:38:58,150
Your Majesty,

824
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:00,670
Prince Xiang's rebellion
has been eradicated.

825
00:39:01,110 --> 00:39:02,990
Seven forts reclaimed and 3000 captured.

826
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:03,880
Great work.

827
00:39:04,550 --> 00:39:06,240
You should be rewarded

828
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:07,760
for your heroic deeds.

829
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,470
I shall betroth you

830
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:11,590
with my only sister,
Princess Royal Rong Yang.

831
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:12,400
What do you think?

832
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:14,320
Much obliged,

833
00:39:15,150 --> 00:39:16,190
but I am engaged.

834
00:39:16,470 --> 00:39:17,150
I must decline.

835
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:34,880
Very well.

836
00:39:37,240 --> 00:39:40,190
I will help you win him over.

837
00:39:56,360 --> 00:39:56,920
Old Madam,

838
00:39:57,070 --> 00:39:58,320
why was a decree sent

839
00:39:58,320 --> 00:39:59,670
to our doorstep?

840
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,880
I bet it's the Floral Banquet.

841
00:40:02,030 --> 00:40:02,800
Si shouldn't have

842
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:04,190
drawn too much attention.

843
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,240
Especially from the Seventh Prince.

844
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,510
Who knows what trouble

845
00:40:08,510 --> 00:40:10,030
awaits us this time?

846
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:11,510
The Old Madam is here.

847
00:40:17,990 --> 00:40:19,800
A decree by His Majesty.

848
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:24,400
"Jiang Si, the daughter
of the Count of Dongping,

849
00:40:24,630 --> 00:40:25,630
is kind and honest

850
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:27,070
and has outstanding qualities.

851
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:29,150
It was delightful
to learn of her virtues.

852
00:40:29,510 --> 00:40:30,840
My seventh son, Jin,

853
00:40:30,990 --> 00:40:32,320
has reached the age for marriage.

854
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:34,360
He must marry a virtuous wife.

855
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,760
I hereby

856
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,670
betroth her to the Seventh Prince.

857
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:39,630
A wedding shall be held
on an auspicious date.

858
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,800
The arrangement shall be executed."

859
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:43,440
I am grateful

860
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,840
for His Majesty's grace.

861
00:40:50,360 --> 00:40:51,070
Miss Jiang Si,

862
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:52,070
please accept the decree.

863
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,400
Congratulations, Miss Jiang Si.

864
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:02,590
Many thanks.

865
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,800
Farewell, Your Excellency.

